      & \operatorname *{lim} D \ar [dl, "\lambda _j"']\ar [dr, "\lambda _k"] & \\
      Dj\ar [rr, "Df"'] && Dk
    \end {tikzcd}


 commute for all j\xrightarrow {f} k\in  J, i.e. the equality 




